WAR GAMES SERVER

A Fictional world Theater with realistic ops

GOALS:
 true to life comms and procedures within the realm of DCS
 Fictional CAG, CSG, and world events
 tools available for flight planning and logging
 Server wide coalition based LotATC and SRS to allow for controller groups to join for practice or mission controlling
 coalition based combined arms access for ground forces groups ( ARTY, TANKS, JTAC, etc.)
 discord split to allow coalition based coordination and secure comms
 

